servation times\ndo. Thus, it can be reasonable to rely on published time scales as long as\ncalibration uncertainties are not known.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 28 Mar 2019 09:55:06 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-03-29"}
