tatistical similarities indicate that the Galactic FRB 200428 and FRBs seen at\ncosmological distances can be treated as scaled-up solar radio bursts.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 28 Mar 2019 11:19:45 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 16 Dec 2020 07:38:28 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-01-06"}
