/dynamics of the $XYZ$ states. In terms of the recent $P_c$ states,\nthe lattice simulations of the charmed baryon and anti-charmed meson scattering\nare badly needed. We shall also discuss some important states which may be\nsearched for at BESIII, BelleII and LHCb in the coming years.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 28 Mar 2019 13:52:59 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 1 Apr 2019 12:14:46 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-06-11"}
